'''Tom Whalen''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed [[Rorr'hn of Drgi]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the 16 years and older category. He was 21 at the time his entry was published.<ref name="G7">{{GalaxyCite|7|Design An Alien}}</ref>

